93static int get_method(double h, double a) {
94 int ihint, iaint, i;
95
96 ihint = 14;
97 iaint = 7;
98
99 for (i = 0; i < 14; i++) {
100 if (h <= HRANGE[i]) {
101 ihint = i;
102 break;
103 }
104 }
105
106 for (i = 0; i < 7; i++) {
107 if (a <= ARANGE[i]) {
108 iaint = i;
109 break;
110 }
111 }
112 return SELECT_METHOD[iaint * 15 + ihint];
113}

116static double owens_t_norm1(double x) {
117 return erf(x / sqrt(x: 2)) / 2;
118}
119
120
121static double owens_t_norm2(double x) {
122 return erfc(x / sqrt(x: 2)) / 2;
123}
124
125
126static double owensT1(double h, double a, double m) {
127 int j = 1;
128 int jj = 1;
129
130 double hs = -0.5 * h * h;
131 double dhs = exp(x: hs);
132 double as = a * a;
133 double aj = a / (2 * M_PI);
134 double dj = expm1(x: hs);
135 double gj = hs * dhs;
136
137 double val = atan(x: a) / (2 * M_PI);
138
139 while (1) {
140 val += dj*aj / jj;
141
142 if (m <= j) {
143 break;
144 }
145 j++;
146 jj += 2;
147 aj *= as;
148 dj = gj - dj;
149 gj *= hs / j;
150 }
151
152 return val;
153}

156static double owensT2(double h, double a, double ah, double m) {
157 int i = 1;
158 int maxi = 2 * m + 1;
159 double hs = h * h;
160 double as = -a * a;
161 double y = 1.0 / hs;
162 double val = 0.0;
163 double vi = a*exp(x: -0.5 * ah * ah) / sqrt(x: 2 * M_PI);
164 double z = (ndtr(a: ah) - 0.5) / h;
165
166 while (1) {
167 val += z;
168 if (maxi <= i) {
169 break;
170 }
171 z = y * (vi - i * z);
172 vi *= as;
173 i += 2;
174 }
175 val *= exp(x: -0.5 * hs) / sqrt(x: 2 * M_PI);
176
177 return val;
178}

181static double owensT3(double h, double a, double ah) {
182 double aa, hh, y, vi, zi, result;
183 int i;
184
185 aa = a * a;
186 hh = h * h;
187 y = 1 / hh;
188
189 vi = a * exp(x: -ah * ah/ 2) / sqrt(x: 2 * M_PI);
190 zi = owens_t_norm1(x: ah) / h;
191 result = 0;
192
193 for(i = 0; i<= 30; i++) {
194 result += zi * C[i];
195 zi = y * ((2 * i + 1) * zi - vi);
196 vi *= aa;
197 }
198
199 result *= exp(x: -hh / 2) / sqrt(x: 2 * M_PI);
200
201 return result;
202}

205static double owensT4(double h, double a, double m) {
206 double maxi, hh, naa, ai, yi, result;
207 int i;
208
209 maxi = 2 * m + 1;
210 hh = h * h;
211 naa = -a * a;
212
213 i = 1;
214 ai = a * exp(x: -hh * (1 - naa) / 2) / (2 * M_PI);
215 yi = 1;
216 result = 0;
217
218 while (1) {
219 result += ai * yi;
220
221 if (maxi <= i) {
222 break;
223 }
224
225 i += 2;
226 yi = (1 - hh * yi) / i;
227 ai *= naa;
228 }
229
230 return result;
231}

234static double owensT5(double h, double a) {
235 double result, r, aa, nhh;
236 int i;
237
238 result = 0;
239 r = 0;
240 aa = a * a;
241 nhh = -0.5 * h * h;
242
243 for (i = 1; i < 14; i++) {
244 r = 1 + aa * PTS[i - 1];
245 result += WTS[i - 1] * exp(x: nhh * r) / r;
246 }
247
248 result *= a;
249
250 return result;
251}

254static double owensT6(double h, double a) {
255 double normh, y, r, result;
256
257 normh = owens_t_norm2(x: h);
258 y = 1 - a;
259 r = atan2(y: y, x: (1 + a));
260 result = normh * (1 - normh) / 2;
261
262 if (r != 0) {
263 result -= r * exp(x: -y * h * h / (2 * r)) / (2 * M_PI);
264 }
265
266 return result;
267}

270static double owens_t_dispatch(double h, double a, double ah) {
271 int index, meth_code;
272 double m, result;
273
274 if (h == 0) {
275 return atan(x: a) / (2 * M_PI);
276 }
277 if (a == 0) {
278 return 0;
279 }
280 if (a == 1) {
281 return owens_t_norm2(x: -h) * owens_t_norm2(x: h) / 2;
282 }
283
284 index = get_method(h, a);
285 m = ORD[index];
286 meth_code = METHODS[index];
287
288 switch(meth_code) {
289 case 1:
290 result = owensT1(h, a, m);
291 break;
292 case 2:
293 result = owensT2(h, a, ah, m);
294 break;
295 case 3:
296 result = owensT3(h, a, ah);
297 break;
298 case 4:
299 result = owensT4(h, a, m);
300 break;
301 case 5:
302 result = owensT5(h, a);
303 break;
304 case 6:
305 result = owensT6(h, a);
306 break;
307 default:
308 result = NAN;
309 }
310
311 return result;
312}

315double owens_t(double h, double a) {
316 double result, fabs_a, fabs_ah, normh, normah;
317
318 if (cephes_isnan(h) || cephes_isnan(a)) {
319 return NAN;
320 }
321
322 /* exploit that T(-h,a) == T(h,a) */
323 h = fabs(x: h);
324
325 /*
326 * Use equation (2) in the paper to remap the arguments such that
327 * h >= 0 and 0 <= a <= 1 for the call of the actual computation
328 * routine.
329 */
330 fabs_a = fabs(x: a);
331 fabs_ah = fabs_a * h;
332
333 if (fabs_a == INFINITY) {
334 /* See page 13 in the paper */
335 result = 0.5 * owens_t_norm2(x: h);
336 }
337 else if (h == INFINITY) {
338 result = 0;
339 }
340 else if (fabs_a <= 1) {
341 result = owens_t_dispatch(h, a: fabs_a, ah: fabs_ah);
342 }
343 else {
344 if (fabs_ah <= 0.67) {
345 normh = owens_t_norm1(x: h);
346 normah = owens_t_norm1(x: fabs_ah);
347 result = 0.25 - normh * normah -
348 owens_t_dispatch(h: fabs_ah, a: (1 / fabs_a), ah: h);
349 }
350 else {
351 normh = owens_t_norm2(x: h);
352 normah = owens_t_norm2(x: fabs_ah);
353 result = (normh + normah) / 2 - normh * normah -
354 owens_t_dispatch(h: fabs_ah, a: (1 / fabs_a), ah: h);
355 }
356 }
357
358 if (a < 0) {
359 /* exploit that T(h,-a) == -T(h,a) */
360 return -result;
361 }
362
363 return result;
364}
